# Detecting Nmap Network Scans with Sysmon and Splunk

## Objective
Detect network scanning activity using Sysmon logs.

## Lab Environment

Attacker Machine
- Kali Linux
- Nmap scanning

Victim Machine
- Windows 10
- Sysmon installed

SIEM
- Splunk

## Attack Simulation

Command used:

nmap -sS 192.168.28.10

## Logs Generated

Sysmon Event ID 3

## Detection Query

index=sysmon EventCode=3

